snippet.title: Key: Maze of Illusions | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
On 12/15 Key: Maze of Illusions will be available to play on Steam and the Play Store!

Will you be able to help Zeno in his adventure? Well, that remains to be seen... Hurry and add the Key to your WISHLIST on Steam and the PRE-REGISTRATION on Play Store!

As always, we want to thank all of you who support us in every way. Right now, your support is even more precious, so please share so more people can learn about and be interested in Key!

• Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1652090/Key_Maze_of_Illusions/

• Play Store Page: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.SieneGames.KeyMoI

• Siene Games on Twitter: https://twitter.com/siene_games

• Siene Games on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SieneGames/

• Siene Games on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sienegames/

Come venture into a dangerous dungeon full of enemies and deadly traps with Key: Maze of Illusions! An insane and addictive platform action game. Help Zeno find the keys he needs to explore all the rooms in the dungeon and find out what really happened!
